Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.49,0:00:04.39,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.39,0:00:05.54,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:08.32,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Turn into a teacup!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:11.27,Trixie,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:12.17,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Teacup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:13.57,Trixie,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:14.69,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Teacup!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.27,0:00:16.42,Trixie,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:20.01,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Starlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.17,0:00:23.22,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I can't put a trick that's not working into my act.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:25.13,Trixie,,0,0,0,,How come it's not working?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:28.44,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It could be because you're just yelling "teacup!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:30.56,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,and not picturing it in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:33.29,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah, it could be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:35.13,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What does your tea cup look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:37.00,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What shape is it? What color?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:45.30,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Starlight, I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:48.75,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I did it! I did it! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:51.62,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Teacup!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:53.20,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Teacup!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:54.96,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Teacup! Teacup! Teacup!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:56.95,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Tea cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:00:58.33,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Teacup!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:00:58.92,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Teacup!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:00.05,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Tea cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.04,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You know what you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:03.08,Trixie,,0,0,0,,A tea cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:11.30,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:14.25,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I guess I pictured a tea cup poodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:15.35,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Trixie,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:18.09,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,you ruined my teacakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:19.69,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I just got excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:22.76,Trixie,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I did a transfiguration spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:24.44,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Real magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:27.03,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Come on, be impressed by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:28.95,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Yay, Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:32.09,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You're so great at magic and having good hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:36.00,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Good job, Trix.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:39.53,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But I was baking these to give to Twilight and the girls for their friendship retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:41.69,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie gave me a recipe and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:44.45,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Oh, you need some snacks to give to Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:46.29,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I've got you covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:53.35,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Problem solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:01:59.60,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:43.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I am so excited for this friendship retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:47.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't remember the last time we all got to hang out without having to save Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:50.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well, we are awesome,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:53.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,but technically we weren't the last ponies to save Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I was speaking in a broader sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't wanna come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.64,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have got three new comics to get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:04.57,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And I promised Trixie we practice more magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.24,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It might be better if the castle was empty,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:08.40,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,if you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:10.91,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:12.16,Trixie,,0,0,0,,If anything breaks,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:14.38,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Starlight will just go back in time and fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:18.34,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:21.61,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,We'll take good care of the castle while you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:23.85,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Have fun on your friendship retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:27.82,Trixie,,0,0,0,,What in Equestria is a friendship retreat anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:30.66,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,They gonna bond, share laughs, and if I know them,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.05,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,they gonna sing a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:35.54,Trixie,,0,0,0,,We are gonna have so much more fun than them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.46,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Twilight, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.62,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Starlight has something for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.88,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Here, I… brought you snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:50.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, how… thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thanks. We will…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:54.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,not get hungry on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:56.44,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It was supposed to be tea cakes, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:58.43,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,it's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.21,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Have a great time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:01.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.24,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Okay, Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.98,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What kind of spells did you want to work on next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.11,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:16.58,Trixie,,0,0,0,,every self-respecting magician has a disappearing act.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:18.32,Trixie,,0,0,0,,So, maybe we could start with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:20.99,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Nothing just disappears,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.31,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,so that's technically a teleportation spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:25.24,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And those are pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.62,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should start with something smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.19,Trixie,,0,0,0,,No-no-no-no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:31.91,Trixie,,0,0,0,,The Great and Powerful Trixie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.69,Trixie,,0,0,0,,goes big or not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:36.85,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Just tell me how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:40.71,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I've always found magic is tied to my emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:44.28,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Whatever I'm feeling fuels whatever I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:47.02,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And the stronger I'm feeling the stronger the magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:48.88,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:52.46,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Like when you were so upset that cutie marks took away your friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:55.46,Trixie,,0,0,0,,your magic was strong enough to enslave an entire village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:57.88,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:04:59.94,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Thanks for bringing that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.34,Trixie,,0,0,0,,See? I'm already learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:05.82,Trixie,,0,0,0,,If anypony is gonna teach me how to do a disappearing spell…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.15,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Teleportation spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:08.33,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.91,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I'm complimenting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:10.66,Trixie,,0,0,0,,And me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.77,Trixie,,0,0,0,,We can do this 'cause we're amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.69,Trixie,,0,0,0,,and magic is friendship and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.70,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I guesss we can give it a whirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:21.96,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Now, we just need to find you something to teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:23.45,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:24.63,Trixie,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:28.82,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Let's pick something… I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:29.64,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,not living?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.99,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I mean it won't be as impressive,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.04,Trixie,,0,0,0,,but okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:35.08,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Teach away, mini-Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:39.69,SomeponyBlueOnYellow,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Manehattan Escapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:42.25,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm going to start with a facial,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and then get my hooves done and…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:46.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not that kind of retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:48.68,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Isn't it called "Manehattan Escapes",
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:51.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,because it's a deluxe spa, where you can escape all of your troubles?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:52.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:55.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's because we get locked in the room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and we get to solve puzzles and riddles in order to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:03.33,SomeponyBlueOnYellow,,0,0,0,,The clues will lead you to a key to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Team building!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:07.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:08.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,This could be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:09.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:12.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Some of the brightest minds of Equestria put together these puzzles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:15.32,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm just happy to be with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:16.52,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.12,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'm not great at solving riddles,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:21.10,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,but I'm super great at cheering other ponies on when they do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.37,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Go us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:24.95,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.59,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, woohoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But just so we know…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.75,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Exactly how long we will be locked in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:36.42,SomeponyBlueOnYellow,,0,0,0,,A group of griffons set the record for the fastest escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.01,SomeponyBlueOnYellow,,0,0,0,,It only took them an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:38.60,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.59,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Griffons barely like each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:45.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're basically the poster ponies for amazing friendships.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.54,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So get your quill ready, bub.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to write a new record.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:53.80,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,If you master this spell before the girls get back,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.59,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,you'd be setting some kind of record.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.47,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Challenge accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:58.07,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:00.73,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,what you wanna do is concentrate on the object
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.28,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,that you want to teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.36,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I gonna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:06.08,Spike,,0,0,0,,All the way over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.83,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Concentrate on teleporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:09.56,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:11.67,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Doing the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.48,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No, Trix, wait, not just!..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.02,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:30.91,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:34.23,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You made Twilight's friendship map disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:36.09,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:37.15,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:40.48,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Well, it was behind the apple, it was bound to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:43.37,Trixie,,0,0,0,,On the plus side, my magic is getting better!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.27,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I made a whole table go poof!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.17,Trixie,,0,0,0,,That was pretty impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.00,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.05,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,We have to get that map back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.72,Trixie,,0,0,0,,We'll find it, no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:55.10,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Twilight will never trust me to be alone in this castle again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.24,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.83,Trixie,,0,0,0,,"Teleport!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.23,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Like you told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:01.01,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:03.53,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to concentrate on the object,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:05.12,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,not just teleporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:06.57,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Well, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:10.16,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You probably should have told me all the steps before you let me do the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:11.94,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I tried…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:16.18,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I… need a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:30.44,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I will be, once I cast a spell to contain my anger in this bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.53,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.55,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Do you see this stormcloud?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.39,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,This has never happened before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:38.71,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,All this magical energy has to go somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:41.14,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,and if I'm not using it to fight a magical duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:44.72,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,or bend my friends' wills to obey my every command…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,Ha, I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.87,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,The point is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:50.70,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I don't know what my magic's going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:53.34,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,So, I'm hoping if I bottle up my anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:56.15,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I won't do who-knows-what to Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:59.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.87,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What choice do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.13,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I've got to get that map back, and,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.97,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna lose Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:06.92,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,If she knew what I was thinking right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:09.23,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,she'd probably never talk to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.87,Spike,,0,0,0,,Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:12.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,you do what you need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:14.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'll see if I can find the map somewhere in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.62,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:29.55,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:34.93,Trixie,,0,0,0,,For a minute I didn't think you were coming back, and that you might be upset with me for some weird reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:38.58,Trixie,,0,0,0,,But then I remembered, you never get mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:44.60,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:46.04,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Not mad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:50.74,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,So, the map is probably in the last place you were thinking of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.19,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Where was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:54.65,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Ooh, great question,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:58.32,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd asked it, like, right after I did the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.86,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:04.15,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.89,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,We'll just take a walk around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.93,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Maybe that'll jog your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:09.38,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Okay, that sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:11.64,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Did you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:12.39,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:16.09,Trixie,,0,0,0,,But I did think we could stop for cinnamon nuts while we're out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.26,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Cinnamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.26,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:21.54,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:22.52,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:27.53,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I've been craving something sweet since I couldn't have any teacakes this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.48,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You got this, Starlight…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:36.09,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Go Twilight, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:44.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You solved that triangley thing mighty fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:47.15,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Uh, does anypony need a purple jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.70,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Plum or bouysenberry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.82,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Don't both those fruits mean purple?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:55.75,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes, but one's a lovely purpley color, one's icky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:57.97,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Just put the gem in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:59.97,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're trying to set a record here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:06.85,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We solved another clue,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.85,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,'cause our friendship is so true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:21.14,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Ah, hello, fillies, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:23.78,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, are those cinnamon nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.17,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Mmm, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:27.11,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I got them from the cart outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:28.67,Trixie,,0,0,0,,They're delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:29.78,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Do you want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:31.97,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a big table, magical map on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:34.01,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,sometimes glowing cutie marks shoot out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.80,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A big ta— Uh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:39.09,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Uh, why in Equestria would something like that be in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:46.21,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Well, I cast a pretty amazing spell that transported it to the last place I was thinking of,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:51.64,Trixie,,0,0,0,,but I might have been thinking about how I'd treat myself to a nice brooch instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:54.22,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, no huge table here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.54,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Uh, still interested in that brooch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:57.25,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.45,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:01.26,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,We don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:03.47,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Twilight and the girls are gonna be back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.83,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But I'm not upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.45,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Where's our next stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.27,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Nope, I ain't seen it.'
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.46,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:17.66,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It's really, really important that we find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:22.23,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And it might be here because somepony was craving apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.91,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I'm still craving them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:27.14,Trixie,,0,0,0,,They go so well with cinnamon nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:31.17,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Oh, them nuts sure do smell good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.06,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Granny Smith, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.25,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,The table?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:42.66,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Well, my eyes ain't what they used to be, but I'd know if a big ol' table done appeared out of thin air!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:54.81,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Darn, I could've sworn it'd be in the ice cream parlor, 'cause it was warm in the castle and I thought I wanted ice cream, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:13:00.30,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should check out the Crystal Empire 'cause Twilight's castle is made out of crystals, so I totally had crystals on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:06.76,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Okay, we better start moving if we want to make it to the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.42,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:13.14,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Because you seem a little, uh, what's the word… "lch-bh-ba".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:17.94,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Nope. I am great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.88,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Did your saddlebag just glow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:20.63,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:21.05,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Gimme!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:21.77,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:22.34,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:22.87,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:23.59,Trixie,,0,0,0,,What's in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.39,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,Cinnamon nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:30.09,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I have had a hankerin' for these all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:31.04,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Uh, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since that Trixie came by with 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:55.19,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Um, why are they looking at me like that…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:05.44,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,You ruined my teacake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.36,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:11.78,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You just had to get Twilight those smelly pretzels!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.34,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Were they your pretzels?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:14.82,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:18.10,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,You don't pay attention when I'm trying to teach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:21.00,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Starlight! Can you help me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.78,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Twilight, can you help me please?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.84,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I've seen those symbols.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:30.52,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:34.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.26,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I've got the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm so impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:44.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm not. I knew we were the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:46.00,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,You are the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.34,Trixie,,0,0,0,,That seems harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:50.60,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Starlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.66,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.66,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Starlight help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:59.10,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm glad Twilight isn't here to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:02.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I wish that Starlight was here to see how strong friendships can be,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:04.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,when we trust each other and work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:07.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You've all taught me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:11.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Friendship used to make me so queasy, queasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:14.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But you made it all so easy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:18.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Now I don't have to say what I'm thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:22.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You already know without even blinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:25.92,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You girls are the apple of my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:29.54,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The race that doesn't end in a tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:33.20,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You are the funnel cake at my fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.22,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,The warm hug of a fuzzy bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:38.24,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Best friends
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:41.16,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Until the end of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:44.54,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We'll have each other's backs
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:47.78,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And let our true selves shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:53.00,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And that's because everything we need
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:56.74,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Is all right here, when we're with our team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.08,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Starlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:02.78,Trixie,,0,0,0,,A spark of magic would be very helpful right about now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.96,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:08.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I simply can't imagine there'd be a day
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:12.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Where I wouldn't want to be walking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:16.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Whatever new problems there may be, may be
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:19.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Our friendship is always the door with the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:23.54,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You are the jewels in my friendship crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:27.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The sparks that make my world go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:30.70,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We bring the best out, that's our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:33.64,Somepony,,0,0,0,,There's no telling how far we'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:35.94,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Best friends
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:38.74,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Until the end of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.06,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We'll have each other's backs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:45.78,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And let our true selves shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:50.56,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And that's because everything we need
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:54.50,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Is all right here, when we're with our team.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:58.62,Somepony,,0,0,0,,That was lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:16:59.72,Somepony,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:02.78,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You know the game isn't over until you turn that key.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:09.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Do we do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.98,Somepony,,0,0,0,,So close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:15.94,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You missed the griffon record by two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:18.82,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Probably you shouldn't have sung that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Aw nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:25.54,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:34.08,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,You just do whatever you want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:36.20,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Starlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:40.80,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,And always have to bring up my dark past!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.40,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you have one, Granny Smith!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:51.24,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I just can't believe you sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:53.24,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You make me so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.24,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I barely even know you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:57.92,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I don't understand why you're all so mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.60,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,They are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:00.80,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:05.47,Trixie,,0,0,0,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:08.33,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm really…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:10.66,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:13.09,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You lost Twilight's map table.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:16.01,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You make jokes like it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:19.66,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It's like you don't even care you could get me in a lot of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.07,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,If we can't find that table,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:23.43,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Twilight's never going to trust me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:24.73,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And the worst part is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:27.32,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,you didn't even say you were sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:30.21,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I… I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:32.52,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I had no idea you felt that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.20,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.07,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.44,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But to be fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:39.64,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you could have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.91,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I did a spell, bottled up my anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.58,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,but when the bottle broke,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.58,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,it infected these three.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:47.79,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:51.11,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I used magic so I wouldn't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:53.88,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I should have guessed that would backfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:55.64,Somepony,,0,0,0,,That's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a slow day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:19:01.88,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was gonna get my dentures cleaned before y'all showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:04.49,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:06.49,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,My nut cart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:10.36,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.60,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,My nut cart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:14.83,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Hang on, don't you work at the spa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:17.54,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,I'm late for my other job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:20.51,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,What? I wear many hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:24.25,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Not gonna lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:26.00,Trixie,,0,0,0,,hearing you and those random ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:29.70,Trixie,,0,0,0,,say all those terrible things about me wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:31.74,Trixie,,0,0,0,,But I needed to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:34.42,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just tell me how you felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:36.62,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to lose you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.62,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:41.44,Trixie,,0,0,0,,It'd take a lot more than that to lose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:44.62,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Our friendship is stronger than a few angry words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.92,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And a magical temper tantrum?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:47.74,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:51.69,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I'd take that over the boring pony you were becoming any day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:57.91,Trixie,,0,0,0,,The Starlight I love is passionate, lively, and yeah, sometimes angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:20:00.36,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Those are my favorite parts of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:04.33,Trixie,,0,0,0,,That, and the fact that you forgive me every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:08.62,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'll forgive you if you forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:09.66,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.62,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I remembered what I was thinking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:16.59,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:18.37,Trixie,,0,0,0,,There's more to it than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:21.26,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about how glad I am to have met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:26.12,Trixie,,0,0,0,,and I remembered our first meeting, here at the Ponyville spa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:28.45,Trixie,,0,0,0,,And now I just have to teleport it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.83,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Nonononononono!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:38.49,Spike,,0,0,0,,A little to the left. Oh, now rotate it just a hair…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:40.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hey girls, how'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:42.75,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:44.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:47.73,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Let's just say I learned a friendship lesson while you were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:51.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You've barely graduated, and you're already taking initiative!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm… so proud…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:58.11,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We learned about team building, and problem solving…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:00.19,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And when not to sing songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We certainly had a good time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:05.07,Rarity,,0,0,0,,but I really was looking forward to a spa day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:09.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and the Ponyville spa's still open! Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:14.29,Trixie,,0,0,0,,We'll meet you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:17.50,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Quick! Do you have a spell that will make the spa ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.57,Trixie,,0,0,0,,forget that the map table was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:23.72,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Haven't you learned anything about using magic to solve your problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:28.86,Trixie,,0,0,0,,No. If we learned that lesson, how will we ever have fun?
